                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110710-9-victim124 t18110710-9-viclabel50"></join>; I lived there at the time the robbery was committed, but I have removed since. It is in the <placeName id="t18110710-9-crimeloc51">parish of Allhallows</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18110710-9-crimeloc51" type="placeName" value="parish of Allhallows"></interp>
